abstract: Book The Isaac Mizrahi Pictures: New York City 1989-1993 by photographer Nick Waplington looks back on past Manhattan fashion and nightlife from more than 20 years ago.

headline.main: Lively Vintage Photos of Supermodels and Superclubs

snippet: “The Isaac Mizrahi Pictures: New York City 1989-1993,” by Nick Waplington, captures a singular era in Manhattan fashion and nightlife.
lead_paragraph: “The Isaac Mizrahi Pictures: New York City 1989-1993,” by Nick Waplington, captures a singular era in Manhattan fashion and nightlife.
